INSERT INTO edc_chemicals (cas_number, chemical_name, common_names, chemical_class, edc_category, hormone_systems_affected, health_effects, common_sources, exposure_routes, bioaccumulation_potential, regulatory_status, epa_data) VALUES
('80-05-7', 'Bisphenol A', '["BPA"]', 'Plasticizer', 'confirmed', '["reproductive", "thyroid", "metabolic"]', 'Estrogen-like effects, reproductive toxicity, thyroid disruption, metabolic disorders, neurodevelopmental effects, increased cancer risk', '["Plastic bottles", "Food can linings", "Thermal paper receipts", "Dental sealants", "Water bottles"]', '["ingestion", "dermal"]', 'moderate', 'Banned in baby bottles (US, EU, Canada), restricted in some products', '{"pubmed_citations": 1707, "key_studies": ["Rubin 2011", "Hafezi 2019"], "regulatory_actions": "FDA banned in baby bottles 2012"}'),
('80-09-1', 'Bisphenol S', '["BPS"]', 'Plasticizer', 'confirmed', '["reproductive", "thyroid"]', 'BPA substitute with similar endocrine disrupting effects, reproductive toxicity', '["BPA-free plastics", "Thermal paper", "Food packaging"]', '["ingestion", "dermal"]', 'moderate', 'Unregulated in most jurisdictions', '{"notes": "BPA replacement with similar concerns"}'),
('620-92-8', 'Bisphenol F', '["BPF"]', 'Plasticizer', 'confirmed', '["reproductive", "thyroid"]', 'BPA substitute with endocrine disrupting properties', '["BPA-free plastics", "Epoxy resins", "Coatings"]', '["ingestion", "dermal"]', 'moderate', 'Unregulated in most jurisdictions', '{"notes": "BPA replacement with similar concerns"}'),
('117-81-7', 'Di(2-ethylhexyl) phthalate', '["DEHP", "DOP"]', 'Plasticizer', 'confirmed', '["reproductive", "thyroid", "metabolic"]', 'Anti-androgenic effects, reproductive toxicity, metabolic disruption, obesity link', '["PVC plastics", "Medical tubing", "Food packaging", "Toys", "Cosmetics"]', '["ingestion", "inhalation", "dermal"]', 'high', 'Banned in children products (US, EU), restricted in medical devices', '{"pubmed_citations": 627, "regulatory_actions": "EU REACH restriction, US CPSC ban in toys"}'),
('84-74-2', 'Dibutyl phthalate', '["DBP"]', 'Plasticizer', 'confirmed', '["reproductive"]', 'Reproductive toxicity, anti-androgenic effects, developmental effects', '["Nail polish", "Adhesives", "Printing inks", "Cosmetics"]', '["dermal", "ingestion", "inhalation"]', 'moderate', 'Restricted in EU cosmetics, banned in children toys', '{"regulatory_actions": "EU cosmetics ban 2004"}');
